{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Merhen Fantasy Action Adventure 'Odile: Black Duckling Tale' is a game that becomes a little duck and grows up by taking away human power and collects multi-endings. Its main features include pretty dot graphics, fairytale-like stories, and interaction with NPCs with fun movements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/sc00.png?t=1731213698\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The full-fledged game begins when a black duck being bullied in the woods follows one of a princess, a shaman, or a hunter into town. Who would you join?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/\uce90\ub9ad\ud130\uc18c\uac1c0_\uc601\uc5b4.png?t=1731213698\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/\uce90\ub9ad\ud130\uc18c\uac1c1_\uc601\uc5b4.png?t=1731213698\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/\uce90\ub9ad\ud130\uc18c\uac1c2_\uc601\uc5b4.png?t=1731213698\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/\uce90\ub9ad\ud130\uc18c\uac1c3_\uc601\uc5b4.png?t=1731213698\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Manipulate the black duck to take human energy. Taking up a lot of energy can kill humans, and sometimes witnesses. If you let them run scared, the black duck could be in danger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/sc05.png?t=1731213698\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Normally no one notices the little duck's covert behavior, but sometimes there are attack NPCs that see through the duck's black magic, resulting in a battle. Run up, down, jump, and roll to avoid the attack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/sc07.png?t=1731213698\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While 'Odile' is a story-heavy game, most of the text is delivered through the NPC's speech bubble without stopping gameplay. SCG dialogue events only come at a level where the story does not interfere with gameplay and helps you immerse yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Perform belt-scrolling action on three stages: the palace, the temple, and the tavern.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And welcome more than 20 multi-endings.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731213698","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/page.bg.jpg?t=1731213698","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/7e33a0a9d1ac8dbcae8f73120bb900465a76e87b/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731213698","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/7e33a0a9d1ac8dbcae8f73120bb900465a76e87b/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731213698","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Merhen Fantasy Action Adventure 'Odile: Black Duckling Tale' is a game that becomes a little duck and grows up by taking away human power and collects multi-endings. Its main features include pretty dot graphics, fairytale-like stories, and interaction with NPCs with fun movements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/sc00.png?t=1731213698\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The full-fledged game begins when a black duck being bullied in the woods follows one of a princess, a shaman, or a hunter into town. Who would you join?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/\uce90\ub9ad\ud130\uc18c\uac1c0_\uc601\uc5b4.png?t=1731213698\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/\uce90\ub9ad\ud130\uc18c\uac1c1_\uc601\uc5b4.png?t=1731213698\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/\uce90\ub9ad\ud130\uc18c\uac1c2_\uc601\uc5b4.png?t=1731213698\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/\uce90\ub9ad\ud130\uc18c\uac1c3_\uc601\uc5b4.png?t=1731213698\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Manipulate the black duck to take human energy. Taking up a lot of energy can kill humans, and sometimes witnesses. If you let them run scared, the black duck could be in danger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/sc05.png?t=1731213698\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Normally no one notices the little duck's covert behavior, but sometimes there are attack NPCs that see through the duck's black magic, resulting in a battle. Run up, down, jump, and roll to avoid the attack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/sc07.png?t=1731213698\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While 'Odile' is a story-heavy game, most of the text is delivered through the NPC's speech bubble without stopping gameplay. SCG dialogue events only come at a level where the story does not interfere with gameplay and helps you immerse yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Perform belt-scrolling action on three stages: the palace, the temple, and the tavern.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And welcome more than 20 multi-endings.</p>","developers":["Sunflo Labs","Solutena Studio"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/header.jpg?t=1731213698","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257069129,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257069129/movie480.mp4?t=1730922309","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257069129/movie_max.mp4?t=1730922309"},"name":"\uc784\uc2dc \ud2b8\ub808\uc77c\ub7ec","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257069129/e3f934590a093b048ef51d566e4d8332ad7859c2/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1730922309","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257069129/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1730922309","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257069129/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1730922309"}},{"highlight":true,"id":257069130,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257069130/movie480.mp4?t=1730922314","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257069130/movie_max.mp4?t=1730922314"},"name":"\ubcf4\uceec\uace1","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257069130/132fbcea6feb6ab476dfa2f42564bdbe1c948a6a/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1730922314","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257069130/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1730922314","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257069130/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1730922314"}}],"name":"Odile: Black Duckling Tale","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul cl